{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"98297-utsheketshe-usindisa-ujuba","title":"UTsheketshe usindisa uJuba","description":"The land is dry and Little Ant is very thirsty. He goes to the river for a drink and is swept away.","language":"isiZulu","langCode":"zu","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Pumla Mdontswa","Zanele Zuma"],"illustrators":["Wiehan de Jager"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"African Storybook Initiative","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/98297-utsheketshe-usindisa-ujuba"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141891/size3/134ad8caa3025116bcdc29245beb43da.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141891/size6/134ad8caa3025116bcdc29245beb43da.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141758/size6/80a5eaa41e8282b279289216a0be8874.jpg","text":"Kusehlobo, ilanga liphumile. Kusehlathini elomile.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141759/size6/b42bde69c9438b987b1802b046f43e7c.jpg","text":"Sekudlule izinsuku eziningi uTsheketshe engenamanzi.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141760/size6/059c59be641f654ca3207a35a6a35bdf.jpg","text":"Ngidinga iconsi lamanzi, noma ngabe liphuma eqabungeni nje.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141761/size6/85595a093c866e71d0019b2f8c9be7f6.jpg","text":"Kodwa akusekho namazolo lawa.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141762/size6/7814a77f591787ae4b967754eea2786f.jpg","text":"“Uma ngingatholi amanzi manje, ngizofa. Kuzomele ngiye kulo mfula engake ngezwa ngawo,” kusho uTsheketshe.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141763/size6/cb5ff30542cdf30c74c9bd60ac835ef8.jpg","text":"“Hhayi bo! Uzomuka nomfula, umfula ugcwele,” kuxwayisa uNgwejeje ohlakaniphile.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141764/size6/25f1761e78950f3d243b1a68c252324d.jpg","text":"Kodwa uTsheketshe wayome kakhulu. “Ngizofa uma ngingatholi manzi,” kusho yena. UTsheketsheke wahamba wayofuna umfula.","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141765/size6/9d4836efe3c5230feffa7f48975fd724.jpg","text":"9/29","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141766/size6/1ecdebe7df69064955a205aafc2046e8.jpg","text":"Wahamba enqamula otshanini obomile nasemagatsheni omile.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141768/size6/68fb9ad4a0f9be9de79aea7f49fc0813.jpg","text":"Wezwa ukuhaza kwamanzi.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141769/size6/f0c63907656b88559379e0632d82bf85.jpg","text":"UTsheketshe wathi, “Ngibonwa yini, amanzi! Waphuza ephindelela.”","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141770/size6/68e1609389d2f358976071630b7391d1.jpg","text":"Uthe engazelele, wangenisa ngamandla umfula. Shwi! Zaya kuTsheketshe.","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141771/size6/4fafe0b010e3cff8e4108c3e94b69548.jpg","text":"Wazama ukubambelela otshanini obomile eduze kwakhe. Amanzi amphonsa le kude.","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141772/size6/93e3c4a1b7728fdfb4fd29096d4a8e44.jpg","text":"“Ngisizeni bo! Ngisizeni bo!”","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141773/size6/b2bc5552befce42e3d837b501a9c2df8.jpg","text":"“Shesha, gibela lapha,” kusho uJuba omhlophe ebambe ukhuni ngomlomo.","words":null},{"n":16,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141774/size6/651ca5247192faeb05e56e97a322e033.jpg","text":"17/29","words":null},{"n":17,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141775/size6/c429467dbcea394992b1e681692f168c.jpg","text":"“Ngizohlala lapha ukuze ngikwazi ukumbonga uJuba,” kusho uTsheketshe.","words":null},{"n":18,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141776/size6/445a53607c9b52c1da005b403aedbfc0.jpg","text":"Ngesikhathi esalindile uTsheketshe, kwaqhamuka abafana ababili bephethe izihlilingi.","words":null},{"n":19,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141777/size6/53c1ec26a6621da8f3703d67554e8622.jpg","text":"“Kunejuba elikhulu elimhlophe eliphuza kulo mfula. Namhlanje, lizoba ukudla kwethu,” kusho omunye wabafana.","words":null},{"n":20,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141778/size6/f14639abcaf79e0e28952c41be795589.jpg","text":"21/29","words":null},{"n":21,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141779/size6/c5ed43fc171accdddc37ff0865224e19.jpg","text":"“Angeke ngibavumele laba bafana babulale uJuba. Yize ngimncane, konje yini nje engingayenza?”","words":null},{"n":22,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141780/size6/ab970c114f6781d0c9040bdd3e4e26b0.jpg","text":"Ngawo lowo mzuzu uJuba wandiza wehlela phansi ukuzophuza.","words":null},{"n":23,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141781/size6/c7921a901dd9692db02f6363696aca42.jpg","text":"24/29","words":null},{"n":24,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141782/size6/933bf05690c9ab563fda05a6e07d6fcc.jpg","text":"UTsheketshe wayesenalo isu.","words":null},{"n":25,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141783/size6/6f6404332890b77e7418f2d60d6e17c5.jpg","text":"Wagxumela onyaweni lomfana wamncinza kakhulu.","words":null},{"n":26,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141784/size6/5f416817e5bbb88cc4e7da3ab37db435.jpg","text":"“Eshuuu!” kukhala umfana egxuma.","words":null},{"n":27,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141785/size6/d92b41dd4d2a64977b767ab8be802d29.jpg","text":"UJuba wethuka wandizela kude. Waphepha kanjaloke uJuba.","words":null},{"n":28,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/141787/size6/6ceb24adf3188200acc101b6f25e2f39.jpg","text":"Wahleka yedwa uTsheketsheke. Wazibongela kanjalo kuJuba.","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":28,"words":184}}